{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 6",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-608117581718487812 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=608106698237805466&sectionId=608117581718487812)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOJsveCdPr_text","label":"ggOJsveCdPr_text","default":"<p>The Invisible Wall No Pill Can Penetrate</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyHdyNY48m_text","label":"ggyHdyNY48m_text","default":"<p>Biofilm is the key to understanding why nothing had worked for Sarah — and why nothing works for millions of Americans cycling through gut health products.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtiQEoMhDY_text","label":"ggtiQEoMhDY_text","default":"<p>When parasites burrow into the intestinal wall, they secrete a sticky, mucus-like matrix around themselves. This biofilm is a fortress. Behind it, parasites are invisible to the immune system, undetectable by lab tests, and completely shielded from every oral supplement.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeCV6ICgbR_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggeCV6ICgbR_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg17M_MfMBN_text","label":"gg17M_MfMBN_text","default":"<p>When you swallow a capsule — any capsule — stomach acid breaks it down. The surviving compounds get absorbed into the bloodstream through the small intestine. By the time anything reaches the lower intestinal wall where parasites burrow, it's been diluted to near-nothing.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjmW0ig-xO_text","label":"ggjmW0ig-xO_text","default":"<p>The parasites behind the biofilm wall never even know you took anything.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsI6ZcWu-i_text","label":"ggsI6ZcWu-i_text","default":"<p>This is why elimination diets provide temporary relief but never resolve the bloating. This is why probiotic after probiotic fails. This is why people try cleanse after cleanse and quit saying \"it didn't work.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDeVCNF9ld_text","label":"ggDeVCNF9ld_text","default":"<p>It's not that the supplements are bad. It's that the oral delivery pathway cannot reach parasites embedded behind biofilm in the intestinal wall.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7LDf-Qh87_text","label":"gg7LDf-Qh87_text","default":"<p>Gary needed something that could bypass the stomach entirely and reach the gut wall directly.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGpBlrdOku_text","label":"ggGpBlrdOku_text","default":"<p>What he found had been hiding in plain sight for a thousand years.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghSAU_L2-C_text","label":"gghSAU_L2-C_text","default":"<p>The Ancient Compound Big Pharma Can't Patent — And Prays You Never Discover</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggE9ybVXbf8_text","label":"ggE9ybVXbf8_text","default":"<p>The compound is called ricinoleic acid. It makes up 90% of castor oil's fatty acid content. It's been used medicinally since ancient Egypt. Hippocrates prescribed it. Your great-grandmother likely had a bottle in her cabinet.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8F9vc699Q_text","label":"gg8F9vc699Q_text","default":"<p>Here's what modern peer-reviewed research confirms:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg47TI_3aVW_text","label":"gg47TI_3aVW_text","default":"<p>✅ Penetrates and dissolves biofilm matrices — breaking apart the protective shield</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7l-bZmrYE_text","label":"gg7l-bZmrYE_text","default":"<p>✅ Stimulates lymphatic drainage in the abdominal cavity by up to 60%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbKX78bFrr_text","label":"ggbKX78bFrr_text","default":"<p>✅ Triggers smooth muscle contractions in the intestinal wall</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdHGvhx2ah_text","label":"ggdHGvhx2ah_text","default":"<p>✅ Crosses tissue barriers when applied topically under sustained pressure</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMRJy8OQm3_text","label":"ggMRJy8OQm3_text","default":"<p>✅ Creates a hostile environment for parasitic organisms in gut wall tissue</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggb_hnfxgci_text","label":"ggb_hnfxgci_text","default":"<p><strong>But here's the critical detail that changes everything:</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggk7ow-v0zJ_text","label":"ggk7ow-v0zJ_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#B22121;\"><strong>You cannot swallow castor oil and get these benefits.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSlhuwBsJI_text","label":"ggSlhuwBsJI_text","default":"<p>When castor oil is ingested, stomach acid converts ricinoleic acid into a simple laxative compound. That's all you get — cramping, diarrhea, and misery. The biofilm-dissolving properties, the lymphatic stimulation, the antimicrobial effects? All destroyed by digestion.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqSrI5rCUq_text","label":"ggqSrI5rCUq_text","default":"<p><strong>Ricinoleic acid must be delivered transdermally — through the skin.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqQj8Itgva_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggqQj8Itgva_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3uURn9i8K_text","label":"gg3uURn9i8K_text","default":"<p>Through the skin, it bypasses stomach acid entirely. It absorbs through the dermal layers, penetrates into the intestinal wall tissue, and arrives at the biofilm matrix intact. Full-strength. Undiluted.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbcOUxipUL_text","label":"ggbcOUxipUL_text","default":"<p>But transdermal delivery requires three specific conditions:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYSu2ZGAfW_text","label":"ggYSu2ZGAfW_text","default":"<p>1. Sustained contact — six to eight hours minimum. Overnight. While the body's temperature rises and pores open.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-yUHcdK2__text","label":"gg-yUHcdK2__text","default":"<p>2. Compression — consistent pressure against the skin increases absorption 2 to 4 times. The castor oil must be pressed into the abdominal skin, not loosely draped.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHS5txqzxC_text","label":"ggHS5txqzxC_text","default":"<p>3. Body heat — heat opens pores and accelerates transdermal delivery. During sleep, core temperature rises naturally. A properly fitted pack captures that heat.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggORDTN0FNc_text","label":"ggORDTN0FNc_text","default":"<p>This is why our grandparents used castor oil PACKS — not pills. Cloth soaked in castor oil, wrapped around the abdomen, worn to bed.<br>They didn't have the science. They just knew it worked. And somewhere between their generation and ours, we forgot.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZMmeptkQd_text","label":"ggZMmeptkQd_text","default":"<p>The System That Made Transdermal Delivery Possible</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9gKAnrV9G_text","label":"gg9gKAnrV9G_text","default":"<p>Sarah's sister Diane found it first — in a gut health community online. Women describing overnight castor oil packs that actually worked. No mess. No complication. Results within weeks.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghdNsf223i_text","label":"gghdNsf223i_text","default":"<p>The product was called Tavio.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEUQoAQZii_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggEUQoAQZii_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnm2nFNJmx_text","label":"ggnm2nFNJmx_text","default":"<p>A purpose-built system engineered for overnight transdermal castor oil delivery:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSKlyQkfA__text","label":"ggSKlyQkfA__text","default":"<p>✅ Organic cotton inner layer — absorbs and holds castor oil evenly without dripping or leaking</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZ0JvWgbrV_text","label":"ggZ0JvWgbrV_text","default":"<p>✅ Leak-proof barrier — sheets stay completely clean. Every night.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaSWmEfj5G_text","label":"ggaSWmEfj5G_text","default":"<p>✅ Adjustable compression wrap — provides sustained pressure for deeper transdermal absorption</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLFMYOHAFI_text","label":"ggLFMYOHAFI_text","default":"<p>✅ Stays in place all night — even for restless sleepers</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMRPP363FY_text","label":"ggMRPP363FY_text","default":"<p>✅ Body heat capture — no external heating pad needed. No auto-shutoff.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjFSXzl7r5_text","label":"ggjFSXzl7r5_text","default":"<p>✅ 60-second application — apply oil, wrap the pack, go to sleep</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoGHTyJXlw_text","label":"ggoGHTyJXlw_text","default":"<p>✅ Reusable for months — one purchase, not a subscription</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguUcWlGBPG_text","label":"gguUcWlGBPG_text","default":"<p>Gary ordered it immediately. Sarah put it on that night.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaES5QSYfw_text","label":"ggaES5QSYfw_text","default":"<p><i>\"I expected some complicated ritual. I applied the oil, wrapped the pack, went to sleep. Took it off in the morning. Sheets clean. That's it. That's the whole thing.\" — </i>Sarah Whitfield</p>"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
    "locales": {}
  }
